General Care Duties
Perform oral hygiene
Dressing and grooming
Assist in feeding residents
Toileting needs
Turning and positioning
Transferring of residents from bed to wheelchair
Perform planned nursing interventions within
their competencies

Residents’ Engagement
Participate in therapeutic activities with the
residents
Participate in conducting daily engagement
activities and exercises with the residents.

Chaperon/Medical Escort
Accompany residents with stable conditions for
clinical appointments or transfers to other
centres or hospital transfers.